Text: Make sure you drink water! Biologically you body can’t break down the molecules without it! I promise it’ll help you fell better. Sending u good vibes :)

Author: boo_snug
Text: Yesterday was like that for me. We had dinner at my parents for their birthdays, plus my grandpa’s. (my brother and I both live away from home.) as much as I am scared to eat sometimes, I still love to cook for others, so I brought a few appetizers, and a veggie tray for me. I grazed lightly through the day but somehow managed to log everything as over 1100+ calories. I’m not sure if it’s correct or not.   Anyways I feel ya 100%. Stop making me eat, people.
